{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c0ffee00-b111-4a11-9c0d-b1111a220001",
    "name": "billing-core (gRPC) \u2014 CDR debug",
    "description": "gRPC test/debug collection for telcobright-billing-core.\n\nServer: localhost:9000 (h2c, TLS OFF).\ngRPC has no message schema in a bare collection \u2014 after importing, open each request and\nattach the service definition via 'Import a .proto file' -> java/src/main/proto/billing.proto\n(service telcobright.billing.v1.RatingService). Then Invoke.\n\nProcessCdrBatch is THE CDR debug entry (drives the same pipeline the Kafka consumer will feed,\nwriting cdr + acc_chargeable + summary_affected in ONE tx). Needs DB creds set on the service\nand telcobright.summary_affected provisioned. With rates not yet served, cdrs are rejected to\ncdrerror (errored>0) \u2014 that still exercises the write path.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
